"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-live-scoring-blitzboks-france-olympics-semi-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999966936684449, \"rank\": 3.3063261179170214e-06, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbLIVE RESULT | France dash Blitzboks' gold medal dream  Look back at the live scoring as the Blitzboks lost 19-5 to France in the semi-finals of the Paris Olympics on Saturday.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999966936684449, \"rank\": 3.3063261179170214e-06, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 218, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919664333, \"rank\": 8.032722920381323e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blitzboks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919664333, \"rank\": 8.032722920381323e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Blitzboks are set for asemi-finalagainst France, knowing that victory would ensure they walk away with either a gold or silver medal at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919664333, \"rank\": 8.032722920381323e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After losing to New Zealand 17-5 in pool play on Wednesday, the Blitzboks hit back in style on Thursday to cause a big upset and ensure they will be playing for a medal at the Stade de France on Saturday.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.554857509413485e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Blitzboks' semi-final against France is scheduled for 15:30 on Saturday afternoon (SA and France time).\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919664333, \"rank\": 8.032722920381323e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0601134943830777e-22, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919664333, \"rank\": 8.032722920381323e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coach Philip Snyman was part of the Olympic squad that earned the bronze medal at Rio 2016, and he hopes to now oversee ahistoric run to the next level.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philip Snyman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When the guys made it through to the quarter-finals, I said to them.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'gents, you must start believing'.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yesterday things did not go our way but you must truly believe.'\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our defence had been good but we could not get the ball back.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tonight our defence system worked well and when we had ball in hand we capitalised.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We even left one or two tries out there.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was still not a perfect performance, but the guys fought for the system, they fought for the jersey and they fought for the country.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really proud of them and they deserve to be in the semi-finals.\\\"\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosko Specman, who scored one of the tries, said afterwards that they did what was needed to stay in the hunt for a podium finish.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1577, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.98607913667413e-13, \"text\": \"Rosko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\"}, {\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Coach Philip (Snyman) asked us one thing in the change room and that was to get the joy back of playing for this team, the same joy we displayed in Monaco,\\\" said Specman.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"score\": 0.991026437877133, \"rank\": 0.009054813394145508, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had some ball to play with and it was joy all over.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are still in the tournament and that is a huge boost of confidence.\\\"\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tristan Leyds added: \\\"We had a tough chat with the boys last night and knew we had to pull it together.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.8724665886853766, \"rank\": 0.14567408188137432, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Japan (who they beat 49-5 earlier on Thursday) was a good start.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9782355802619602, \"rank\": 0.022198253522051625, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We just knew we had to gain some points on the board and get a victory.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We got a second chance against New Zealand and the boys produced a special performance in defence.\\\"\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2284, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.554857509413485e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People back home did not think we had a chance but where there is a will, there is a way.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the guys put it together and got the 'W' against New Zealand.\\\"\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2498, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999992346602, \"rank\": 7.554857509413485e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The boys showed a massive effort.\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This team can pull off big surprises like this one.\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was pretty special.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully, we can pull off another surprise in the semi-final.\\\"\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scorers:  South Africa 47 (35), Japan 5 (0)SA- Tries: Zain Davids, Impi Visser, Ryan Oosthuizen (2), Rosko Specman, Shilton van Wyk (2).\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999227839, \"rank\": 7.556399356889271e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_rugby_union_